  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【游戏介绍】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《独特的友谊 - Special Friendship》是一款2D恐怖治愈冒险游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在雷雨交加的夜晚，名为耶鲁卡的机器人邂逅了一位幽灵少女。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >伴随着雷鸣，两人在充满幻影、玩偶与萤火虫的世界中前进，并建立起不逝的友谊。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“但是，这个世界的人类去了哪里。”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“为什么到处都是玩偶，还对我们进行攻击？”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>这个充满忧郁与崩坏的世界里，究竟隐藏了怎样的真相——</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【游戏特色】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你需要突破重重怪物、消除幻影、收集特殊道具，也将面临疯狂的追击者。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在幽灵少女的陪伴下，一同在这个黑暗狂气的世界中前进吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>本作具有：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >丰富的关卡与解谜，以及特殊追逐战</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可选择的游玩难度，让您更好体验作品的魅力</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >看似无厘头却充满暗示的剧情，激发解析与思考</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >鲜明的主角与可爱互动，让您沉浸于故事的氛围中</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >高中生开发者，个人全原创的音乐与美术，将带给您不一样的美学体验！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【操作指南】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Z/ Space  调查 & 确认</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >↑↓←→ 行走 & 选择</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >↑↓←→+Shift    奔跑</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >结局数量：1</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游玩时长：预计3h+</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DEMO时长：1h左右</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2725600/extras/3841cf55cb315bb8ed9eecfdc929ea26.apng?t=1731410426\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2725600/extras/3841cf55cb315bb8ed9eecfdc929ea26.poster.avif?t=1731410426\" class=\"bb_img\" width=115 height=115 /></picture></span></